  "text": "Alpaca chromosome slides were prepared from peripheral blood lymphocytes of normal alpacas according to standard protocols [CITATION_1] . We used Concanavalin A (Con A from Canavalia ensiformis, 20 µg/ml; Sigma Aldrich) as the mitogen, instead of Pokeweed, because Con A stimulates better proliferation of alpaca blood lymphocytes [CITATION_2] .",
